\/h2>\n    <div class=\"UG_contents\">\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/7dc18625f780eeba_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot01\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/7dc18625f780eeba_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/h5.sinaimg.cn\/upload\/100\/721\/2019\/03\/14\/vote.png\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/7dc18625f780eeba_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#泰国文化部禁止拍摄吻戏#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#泰国文化部禁止拍摄吻戏# 为防止新冠病毒传播，泰国禁止拍摄任何涉及亲密接触的打斗、吻戏、近距离触碰等戏份，如有必须可通过特效来完成。此前，日本相关剧集制作人也透露，在重启拍摄时或需要减少接吻、拥抱、亲热的戏份。#阿乐今日问#：看到这个新闻，你的想法是？ http:\/\/t.cn\/A62APJse ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/e502b26814ada3b2_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot02\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/e502b26814ada3b2_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/9e5389bbly1gezmwfmgefj20p00p078a.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/e502b26814ada3b2_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#美国新冠肺炎确诊数超154万#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【#美国新冠肺炎确诊数超154万#】据约翰斯·霍普金斯大学数据，截至美东时间20日16：55，美国新冠肺炎确诊病例为1547353例，死亡93119例。另据纽约时报统计，过去14天以来，包括得克萨斯州等在内的9个州新增病例出现上升。（央视记者王逢治） ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/18c79c5612667a41_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot03\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n     